Each row is an atomic, executable task. Tasks marked ⚠ in red are security-critical — they directly affect the zero-knowledge encryption model, access control, or data integrity. Complete these with extra care and double-check them during the security audit in Phase 5.
Implementation notes (indented → lines) explain exact APIs, algorithms, values, and edge cases to handle within that task. They are not separate tasks.

