P2-015
Create app/(auth)/layout.tsx — centred single-card layout, no navbar, branded logo at top
☐
P2-016
Create app/(auth)/login/page.tsx — email + password form with React state, calls signIn('credentials'), shows error toast on failure, redirects to /dashboard on success
☐
P2-017
Create app/(auth)/register/page.tsx — name + email + password + confirm-password fields. On submit: POST to /api/auth/register (create below). Validate with Zod client-side before submission.
☐
P2-018
⚠ Create app/api/auth/register/route.ts — POST handler. Zod validate body. Check email not already registered. Hash password with bcrypt (saltRounds=12). Create User in DB. Return 201.
  → Use bcrypt saltRounds=12 — not less. saltRounds=10 is too fast for a vault app.
