P2-021
⚠ Create components/vault/VaultUnlock.tsx — full-screen modal overlay. Password input (type=password). On submit: fetch /api/vault/salt, run deriveVaultKey, call store.unlock(key). Show spinner during PBKDF2 (600k iterations ~1-2s). Show generic 'Unable to unlock' on wrong password with no iteration count hint.
  → Do not reveal attempt counts or lockout thresholds in the UI
  → Use a loading state during key derivation — PBKDF2 at 600k rounds blocks the UI thread, so run it in a short setTimeout(0) to allow the spinner to render first
