P2-002
⚠ Create lib/crypto/vault.ts — export deriveVaultKey(masterPassword: string, saltBase64: string, iterations = 600_000): Promise<CryptoKey>
  → Use crypto.subtle.importKey with algorithm PBKDF2 and usages ['deriveKey']
  → Use crypto.subtle.deriveKey with {name:'PBKDF2', salt, iterations, hash:'SHA-256'} → {name:'AES-GCM', length:256}
  → Set extractable: false — key must never be extractable from memory as raw bytes
